h.\n\n**Evaluating risks and container setup**\n\nI'm considering risks with the old Plexus container and its lifecycle. Running the actual javac might invoke the local JDK, so I want to avoid external processes if I can just retrieve the component. There could be reflection or resource issues from the Plexus components.xml when using native-image. I need to check the dependency tree since the POM parent includes the provided container by default but not transitively. If the test retrieves just the JavacCompiler object, the container default is necessary. I also want to ensure I output a valid JSON object without markdown.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_07a981e67a5b381f016a41746077948190bd88e93a9e3d7ecc\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQXRvxu4XoUpaCH5zAxMa2VU3Qqi6vd48oF7loGjYWZrAdXqN3ovNmifZ7uKVQE3vsXOXFSzKkHB-xVzMf3XW49Ao_L88KrKh5Ao4b3glPZg7XOzO-hepT6i4rQyEI9PZzhSAysTG-wyOqn9dVMaQqH-cxdWdLNYGh7wiZkVk9pcXe9BwlE0E_SwgGhxsZGf0Fw_-KJs3zDU5T6sA9RVAF4ORVlyuub5jO9ES9XZUwkt8T8ODH6TO6S2VpChIhhF2MKWS2ZPXuxz-VaouSWlgjvZXNa7fDmjAZyW4TWeIbaGeL_V5u-tv6ag16tBPey_lM_FbDqiJ3gv8Jj-Gu2eZZs-5gvF31utbcmcQeI9DLA88NCdFVqYxxuGkXv056dZ3KSbqwcwmOBwvAbMBS7oGJGHWDl3VI-2GjfZtcwoXlUvl9DAn9f4z_DvLOInN24EPJycChuu7fBNHzuUcFT7BcsfbUBOQh5rn0RekJmsNbsYOA8Zn408lPUazIiT5PYDecoEqSu48j1xl4QiQjz1dfUSe3sz4V2kl9TLem1weVrykNLHXsEPykyrAZruiXs6o5hHhOa2qX0kd7mEJvdjNSpnoMqr0Xt-iFgFq-t7mNgLBVwxBxV-45IAf7mQbLn8nsHKUKhj9l5ygqTFd-c7Xdfqb3Z3G6FIsZTGwqwGMbxYBWHBmTIuQmdi_cqokqkLC6IvFPO10EX4xkMcdhuaH81mMNGsa-YZHIjjVGzftWadUO3Yjo9DC-YQh-tcgoOqdJlAY5qB3qzJyqH15d5v3OyM6rUV1722gMArxNFhymNPgRIWIRMVPJCLDi7DH0riwF8LjnyelFDLy8Y3PDZKlvrPTTYVgttMURcd4WMh3geZkQNgmWUDSSo-_-fl-YJM804zfln1I6H7cPNaqi27pK2Ad_GaEJEk5ut6cUZ3Sq5JClN991HhMM15MDtMV-felhDCczfR-zrQjTQumR6jyukcI4gBQMHUJv1PJ0b6MrvTfyZNgH2gWQj7kStcaD76bSYaHt69T-hZ8Rl5TW-BKzgE-VRT6fUTMlKafQnHLgZIN83vtXCLr8Ue4KzzXE8RJx0QWcgpGXkQNxddZq8v5JpvoG-s9O1qu2Iqtc_7TmQIad9CSp8Sb6ONwD_DK-FN-DzcG1gfSavcXeiEqUeA05JV5jZ1RpaHundr_R_6E5msyEGRHWqGIrd4oZ